long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Ever wanted to visualise your long-winded chats on messenger with your friends? Say no more! Chat tree for messenger allows you to visualise your messages in a tree format. 

This app (will be) coded in a week by a small team of developers engaging in a mini-hackathon at the University of Sydney: Lewis Watts, Eliza Smedley, Steven Liu and Christine Zhu.

Read more here: https://acenturyandabit.github.io/chattree/
